      "writtenOn": "2020-11-11T17:05:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "i am not sure about this change. The original optimization CL added a significant amount of complexity, and now this one adds even more. That\u0027s a lot of complexity for something that should not exist to begin with (if only spanner provided MAX_PARALLELISM). Now that they seem to be OK letting our cloud projects use it, ideally we revert my CL and use MAX_PARALLELISM instead, which would be much simpler. \n\nin other words, the amount of additional complexity is my original CL + this one. To all of it, you could revert my CL and including its optimization into this CL. It would demonstrate how much complexity we are adding.\n\nAlso, I wonder if it is time to compute longest_common_prefix. It would enable us to split the set of invocations into independent subsets and process them in parallel. ",
      "revId": "856ea36c183378f561dd24549dc5b2fa977be199",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": false,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "8bac841f_b8fd30ea",
        "filename": "/PATCHSET_LEVEL",
        "patchSetId": 2
      },
      "lineNbr": 0,
      "author": {
        "id": 1157909
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-11-11T19:22:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m hesitate to revert your original CL because I think the optimization should help most of the invocations. If revert then we\u0027ll see slowness across the board.\n\nDo you think the complexity overweights the performance improvement?",
      "parentUuid": "b7d2fbf6_e3a60c71",
      "revId": "856ea36c183378f561dd24549dc5b2fa977be199",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "e6bf4401_94320389",
        "filename": "/PATCHSET_LEVEL",
        "patchSetId": 2
      },
      "lineNbr": 0,
      "author": {
        "id": 1114299
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-11-11T19:44:05Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I am advocating for better optimizations (MAX_PARALLELISM, longest_common_prefix). If we do them, then we don\u0027t need this complexity.\n\nI am OK with this CL only if this is temporary. Could you add a TODO with a bug, so that we don\u0027t forget?",
      "parentUuid": "8bac841f_b8fd30ea",
      "revId": "856ea36c183378f561dd24549dc5b2fa977be199",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
